title: RHS Flower Show Tatton Park 2017 Complete 720p WEBRip x264-SOIL
description: RHS Flower Show Tatton Park, 2017 Episode 1 Monty Don and Joe Swift host the first of two visits to the RHS Flower Show, Tatton Park in Cheshire, with Carol Klein, Toby Buckland and Arit Anderson. The team explore the diverse range of show gardens including the ingenious designs for the compact 'back to backs'. Carol celebrates the late summer flowering displays in the floral marquee and shares her guide to getting the best out of your hydrangeas. Monty hails horticulture's next generation of planters and landscapers and Joe quizzes champion growers for the secrets to producing perfect summer fruit and veg. Screenshot: https://extraimage.net/images/2017/07/25/5b7a019a11a5c2e2902220323689427b.jpg /////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// RHS Flower Show Tatton Park, 2017 Episode 2 More highlights from the RHS Flower Show, Tatton Park, as Monty Don, Joe Swift and the team review the gardens created by the finalists in the RHS Young Designer of the Year competition and reveal the winners of the prestigious Best Show Garden and Best Back to Back Garden. Arit Anderson looks at a garden designed to adapt to our changing climate, whilst Carol Klein investigates the rise of cacti and succulents as the must-have house plants. And Monty and Joe take a fun trip down Bus Stop Boulevard to choose their favourite of the revamped bus shelters making their debut at this year's show. Screenshot: https://extraimage.net/images/2017/07/25/23d1b3cd0a28d9487b54e1ef283f3d1d.jpg
